oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Hoyte Andrew "Babe" Borren (1918-2001) with his mule "Mag" planting sorghum on the farm belonging to Oscar Stephens Boyd (1911-1986) and Elizabeth Thomas Boyd (1912-1981). The farm was located in Verona, Tennessee.
